680
00:40:39,573 --> 00:40:41,007
Sabe de uma coisa?

681
00:40:41,465 --> 00:40:42,765
Peguem.

682
00:40:44,078 --> 00:40:45,578
Se matem.

683
00:41:03,163 --> 00:41:05,398
Agora, onde consigo
uma bebida?

684
00:41:06,265 --> 00:41:08,634
